# Flatpaks installed on first boot. One app id per line; # and blank lines ignored.
#
# The KDE app ecosystem (dolphin, kate, kcalc, gwenview, okular, spectacle, ark,
# skanpage, haruna, ...) ships NATIVELY as part of the full Plasma desktop -- see
# build_files/build.sh -- so it is intentionally NOT listed here. This list is only for
# cross-desktop GUI apps that have no place in the base image.
com.github.tchx84.Flatseal
net.nokyan.Resources
org.libreoffice.LibreOffice
it.mijorus.gearlever
com.ranfdev.DistroShelf
